def minimum_subscriptions(n, k, d, a):
    ds = dict()
    s = set()
    ml = float('')
    for i in range(d):
        ds[a[i]] = i
        s.add(a[i])
    ml = min(ml, len(s))
    for i in range(d, n):
        ds[a[i]] = i
        s.add(a[i])
        if ds[a[i - d]] <= i - d:
            s.discard(a[i - d])
        ml = min(ml, len(s))
    return ml
